      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "3. As a mystical token of God’s presence and assistance with them, and of their victory; or as a mean by God’s appointment contributing to their good success, as the like posture of Moses lifting up his hand was, ",
        "children": []
